that's in your head. not mine.

516
00:24:15.997 --> 00:24:17.832
You don't even know
my real name.

517
00:24:17.999 --> 00:24:20.126
[gentle dramatic music playing]

518
00:24:20.293 --> 00:24:21.627
So tell me then.

519
00:24:26.340 --> 00:24:27.633
Jarita.

520
00:24:29.635 --> 00:24:30.761
Hmm.

521
00:24:33.431 --> 00:24:34.473
[music fades]

522
00:24:34.640 --> 00:24:37.518
[traffic humming]

523
00:24:37.685 --> 00:24:39.604
[insects chirring]

524
00:24:42.231 --> 00:24:45.484
[dramatic music playing]

525
00:24:51.032 --> 00:24:52.408
Stefano house.

526
00:24:54.744 --> 00:24:55.995
He's got some security.

527
00:24:56.913 --> 00:24:58.122
But nothin' too heavy.

528
00:25:07.381 --> 00:25:10.176
[siren wailing in distance]

529
00:25:13.846 --> 00:25:16.140
Kanan ain't tell me
his mama fine.

530
00:25:16.974 --> 00:25:18.410
Who are you. where the fuck
you come from.

531
00:25:18.434 --> 00:25:19.727
and what you and my son doin'?

532
00:25:19.894 --> 00:25:22.980
[singsong] Kanan fine mama
got questions.

533
00:25:23.147 --> 00:25:25.816
I ain't come here to compare
pedicures. nigga.

534
00:25:26.275 --> 00:25:27.443
I need to understand you

535
00:25:27.610 --> 00:25:29.090
and what the fuck
you think you doin'.

536
00:25:29.528 --> 00:25:31.155
I don't answer to you. ma'am.

537
00:25:31.906 --> 00:25:33.324
I'm only meetin' you
outta respect

538
00:25:33.491 --> 00:25:35.691
'cause I know you meant
somethin' out here for a minute.

539
00:25:37.370 --> 00:25:38.788
But you must've got it confused

540
00:25:38.955 --> 00:25:41.582
if you think you gon'
interrogate me on some shit.

541
00:25:44.585 --> 00:25:46.254
It's always uncomfortable

542
00:25:46.420 --> 00:25:48.381
when there's a woman
in the game.

543
00:25:49.382 --> 00:25:50.883
See. for niggas.

544
00:25:51.050 --> 00:25:53.219
the hustle about
two things only:

545
00:25:53.844 --> 00:25:55.304
bitches and money.

546
00:25:56.389 --> 00:25:59.141
That's the understanding
we all got between us men.

547
00:26:00.142 --> 00:26:02.186
I know what that nigga
on that other corner thinkin'

548
00:26:02.311 --> 00:26:04.355
'cause he thinkin'
the same as me.

549
00:26:04.855 --> 00:26:07.525
Bitches and money.
money and bitches.

550
00:26:07.817 --> 00:26:08.817
That's all.

551
00:26:09.819 --> 00:26:12.321
It's different when there's
a lady on the other side.

552
00:26:13.030 --> 00:26:14.824
'Cause you ain't checkin'
for bitches.

553
00:26:16.909 --> 00:26:18.411
That ain't why you in it.

554
00:26:19.078 --> 00:26:20.913
You on some other shit.

555
00:26:22.415 --> 00:26:24.542
That mean I don't know
what you thinkin'.

556
00:26:26.877 --> 00:26:28.504
And that don't feel good.

557
00:26:30.298 --> 00:26:32.341
You won't ever know
what I'm thinkin'. nigga.

558
00:26:33.634 --> 00:26:35.469
That's what you need
to recognize.

559
00:26:36.637 --> 00:26:38.347
I'm not on these blocks no more.

560
00:26:38.472 --> 00:26:39.682
but I am these blocks.

561
00:26:40.433 --> 00:26:41.684
You understand what I'm sayin'?

562
00:26:41.851 --> 00:26:43.185
[tense music playing]

563
00:26:43.352 --> 00:26:45.813
I'm known... and I know.

564
00:26:46.731 --> 00:26:48.251
And as long as you fuckin'
wit' my son.

565
00:26:48.399 --> 00:26:49.942
I'ma be watching you.

566
00:26:51.110 --> 00:26:52.361
But you right.

567
00:26:53.529 --> 00:26:55.323
I ain't thinkin' 'bout bitches.

568
00:26:55.948 --> 00:26:57.616
All I think about's money.

569
00:26:58.909 --> 00:27:01.162
And ain't nobody get between
me and my money.

570
00:27:01.329 --> 00:27:03.664
[music intensifies]

571
00:27:05.708 --> 00:27:06.459
[music fades]

572
00:27:06.625 --> 00:27:08.002
He here most days.

573
00:27:08.669 --> 00:27:10.087
This his favorite spot.

574
00:27:11.630 --> 00:27:13.632
Got any questions or anything?

575
00:27:14.467 --> 00:27:15.634
Thoughts?

576
00:27:17.678 --> 00:27:19.055
Is what it is.

577
00:27:20.639 --> 00:27:22.199
Far be it for a humble-ass nigga
like me

578
00:27:22.350 --> 00:27:24.226
to tell professionals
like yourselves

579
00:27:24.393 --> 00:27:26.020
how to do this shit. but...

580
00:27:26.979 --> 00:27:28.898
you only gonna get
one crack at this work.

581
00:27:29.065 --> 00:27:31.067
[dramatic music playing]

582
00:27:31.233 --> 00:27:32.568
Fuck that up...

583
00:27:33.611 --> 00:27:35.446
you ain't gonna make it
back to Tennessee.

584
00:27:36.697 --> 00:27:38.032
[car engine starts]

585
00:27:43.871 --> 00:27:45.539
[music fades]

586
00:27:45.706 --> 00:27:47.541
That was you that hit us.
though.

587
00:27:47.708 --> 00:27:48.876
on 150.

588
00:27:54.048 --> 00:27:56.217
You ain't even got work
out here no more.

589
00:27:56.967 --> 00:27:58.427
Why you fuckin' wit' our corner?

590
00:27:58.594 --> 00:28:00.429
'Cause you're out there
and I'm not. nigga.

591
00:28:03.057 --> 00:28:06.227
You salty 'cause your son still
makin' money without you.

592
00:28:06.352 --> 00:28:08.562
I don't like nobody
makin' money without me.

593
00:28:09.730 --> 00:28:11.565
That's how this shit works. son.

594
00:28:11.732 --> 00:28:13.484
[grim music playing]

595
00:28:13.651 --> 00:28:14.735
Way I see it.

596
00:28:15.736 --> 00:28:17.780
any dollar y'all niggas
stack out here

597
00:28:17.947 --> 00:28:19.573
is a dollar y'all takin'
from me.

598
00:28:20.116 --> 00:28:21.516
And that ain't never
gon' sit right.

599
00:28:21.575 --> 00:28:24.286
Our money's
Stefano Marchetti's money.

600
00:28:25.162 --> 00:28:26.497
But you know that already.

601
00:28:28.165 --> 00:28:30.668
No matter where the fuck I am.
I'm here.

602
00:28:31.919 --> 00:28:34.380
I'm here. there.
and everywhere. nigga.

603
00:28:38.134 --> 00:28:39.969
You could tell Kanan
the same shit.

604
00:28:47.309 --> 00:28:48.853
[music fades]

605
00:28:49.019 --> 00:28:52.731
[from inside Cafe Vous]
♪ Real bad. real bad ♪

606
00:28:52.898 --> 00:28:55.609
[fades] ♪ I know I got it bad ♪

607
00:28:58.446 --> 00:29:02.408
[dark. ominous music playing]

608
00:29:06.829 --> 00:29:08.914
[engine revving]

609
00:29:09.081 --> 00:29:11.125
[tires screeching]

610
00:29:11.250 --> 00:29:13.419
-[whimpering]
-Get the fuck in!

611
00:29:13.586 --> 00:29:15.066
Please. take everything.
I don't care.

612
00:29:15.129 --> 00:29:16.172
We takin' you. bitch.

613
00:29:16.338 --> 00:29:17.548
[whimpering]

614
00:29:18.674 --> 00:29:20.968
Please don't hurt me.
I'll do whatever you want.

615
00:29:21.427 --> 00:29:23.179
[Kanan] That's good. baby.

616
00:29:24.638 --> 00:29:26.724
'Cause we gon' need you
to do some shit.

617
00:29:26.891 --> 00:29:28.767
[gasps. exhales]

618
00:29:28.934 --> 00:29:31.270
[tires screeching]

619
00:29:32.771 --> 00:29:33.856
[coughs]

620
00:29:34.482 --> 00:29:36.609
Shirley was waterin' down
these bottles.

621
00:29:37.443 --> 00:29:38.694
Tricky-ass broad.

622
00:29:38.861 --> 00:29:40.130
["Impatient" playing softly
in Cafe Vous]

623
00:29:40.154 --> 00:29:41.405
[Juke] You want somethin' else?

624
00:29:42.239 --> 00:29:45.659
Probably better for me to drink
the weak shit anyway.

625
00:29:48.871 --> 00:29:49.997
[sighs]

626
00:29:50.456 --> 00:29:51.457
Yo.

627
00:29:53.918 --> 00:29:55.669
Been talkin' to that detective.

628
00:29:57.171 --> 00:29:58.339
Garcia.

629
00:30:01.634 --> 00:30:03.677
Fuck you doin'
talkin' to police?

630
00:30:05.513 --> 00:30:08.933
He tryin' to find out
who put down Howard. so...

631
00:30:10.768 --> 00:30:12.186
I ain't tell him shit.

632
00:30:12.353 --> 00:30:13.437
Obviously.

633
00:30:13.729 --> 00:30:16.440
But he's still messin' with me

634
00:30:16.607 --> 00:30:19.068
so I'm tryin' to get him
to leave me the fuck alone.

635
00:30:21.987 --> 00:30:23.447
I can hit up the new lawyer.

636
00:30:24.365 --> 00:30:25.824
Get him to make a few calls.

637
00:30:27.034 --> 00:30:29.578
Or send a letter or some shit.

638
00:30:30.287 --> 00:30:31.830
Thing is...

639
00:30:31.997 --> 00:30:34.875
I feel like maybe Garcia
could help us.

640
00:30:35.709 --> 00:30:37.002
He know things

641
00:30:37.169 --> 00:30:39.213
and he can find shit out.

642
00:30:39.630 --> 00:30:40.965
Keep us a step ahead.

643
00:30:42.174 --> 00:30:44.176
I started paying him
to step the fuck off.

644
00:30:44.301 --> 00:30:46.303
-[groans]
-And also...

645
00:30:46.470 --> 00:30:47.888
give me information.

646
00:30:49.682 --> 00:30:51.183
You're a wild girl. Juke.

647
00:30:51.892 --> 00:30:53.269
Hittin' off police.

648
00:30:54.311 --> 00:30:56.431
Here I am. trying to steer you
away from all this shit

649
00:30:57.064 --> 00:30:58.899
and you done turned gangster
on me.

650
00:31:01.277 --> 00:31:02.444
I'm short. though.

651
00:31:02.611 --> 00:31:03.737
[dramatic music playing]

652
00:31:03.862 --> 00:31:06.115
He want more
than I got right now.

653
00:31:06.615 --> 00:31:07.866
So you hittin' off this cop

654
00:31:07.992 --> 00:31:09.910
but you don't got enough
to pay him off proper.

655
00:31:10.411 --> 00:31:11.954
How that playin' out for you?

656
00:31:12.413 --> 00:31:13.581
Not good.

657
00:31:14.415 --> 00:31:17.710
Cop on the take
ain't the nigga you wanna short.

658
00:31:17.876 --> 00:31:18.919
[inhales sharply]

659
00:31:19.753 --> 00:31:23.465
Maybe... you could help me out
a little bit

660
00:31:23.632 --> 00:31:24.633
'til I can cover it.

661
00:31:27.261 --> 00:31:29.722
Your deal. your debt. [sighs]

662
00:31:30.889 --> 00:31:32.569
You gotta figure that shit out
on your own.

663
00:31:32.641 --> 00:31:34.059
[sighs] I'll pay you back
the money.

664
00:31:34.226 --> 00:31:36.520
And maybe he got shit
you wanna know too.

665
00:31:37.062 --> 00:31:38.915
I already got enough going on
with these police.

666
00:31:38.939 --> 00:31:40.232
I don't need no more.

667
00:31:43.652 --> 00:31:44.903
Can't lie. though...

668
00:31:46.572 --> 00:31:48.115
you makin' moves out here.

669
00:31:51.035 --> 00:31:52.620
Chip off the old fuckin' block.

670
00:31:55.456 --> 00:31:57.249
[music fades]

671
00:31:57.374 --> 00:31:59.394
["Escape (The Pina Colada Song)"
[by Rupert Holmes playing]

672
00:31:59.418 --> 00:32:02.421
-♪ If you like pina coladas ♪
-[slurred singing with song]

673
00:32:02.588 --> 00:32:05.090
♪ And gettin' caught
In the rain ♪

674
00:32:06.133 --> 00:32:09.053
♪ If you're not into yoga ♪

675
00:32:09.178 --> 00:32:11.680
♪ If you have half a brain ♪

676
00:32:12.431 --> 00:32:15.643
♪ If you like makin' love
At midnight ♪

677
00:32:15.809 --> 00:32:18.812
♪ In the dunes of the Cape ♪

678
00:32:18.979 --> 00:32:21.940
♪ You're the one
That I look for ♪

679
00:32:22.816 --> 00:32:25.319
♪ Write to me and escape ♪

680
00:32:27.321 --> 00:32:28.656
♪♪

681
00:32:28.781 --> 00:32:30.908
There's my favorite girl.

682
00:32:34.495 --> 00:32:36.121
[music volume lowers]

683
00:32:36.288 --> 00:32:37.289
[sniffs]

684
00:32:39.708 --> 00:32:41.126
Gonna make me beg for it?

685
00:32:41.293 --> 00:32:43.462
[on stereo] ♪ I didn't think
About my lady ♪

686
00:32:43.629 --> 00:32:46.465
♪ I know that sounds
Kinda mean ♪

687
00:32:46.632 --> 00:32:48.425
[man sniffs. sighs]

688
00:32:49.176 --> 00:32:50.177
[man chuckles]

689
00:32:50.928 --> 00:32:53.889
♪ Had fallen into
The same old dull routine ♪

690
00:32:54.014 --> 00:32:56.183
♪ So I wrote to the paper ♪

691
00:32:56.350 --> 00:32:57.393
[sniffs]

692
00:32:57.559 --> 00:32:59.311
♪ Took out a personal ad ♪

693
00:33:00.521 --> 00:33:02.272
♪ And though I'm nobody's poet ♪

694
00:33:02.398 --> 00:33:03.816
Gonna do this...

695
00:33:03.982 --> 00:33:06.527
and then I'm gonna do you.

696
00:33:07.653 --> 00:33:09.029
[sniffs loudly]

697
00:33:10.197 --> 00:33:11.323
Oh-ho-ho!

698
00:33:11.490 --> 00:33:13.826
[laughs] Wow.

699
00:33:15.077 --> 00:33:17.079
[laughs]

700
00:33:17.246 --> 00:33:20.165
[sinister music playing]

701
00:33:20.332 --> 00:33:21.083
What the fuck?

702
00:33:21.250 --> 00:33:23.001
[gasping softly]

703
00:33:23.544 --> 00:33:24.544
What?

704
00:33:25.462 --> 00:33:27.923
What? [coughing]

705
00:33:29.133 --> 00:33:31.301
[gasping]

706
00:33:32.720 --> 00:33:35.347
[gagging. coughing]

707
00:33:40.352 --> 00:33:41.353
Oh God.

708
00:33:44.732 --> 00:33:46.525
[whispers] Oh. Oh no.

709
00:33:52.614 --> 00:33:54.199
[music intensifies]

710
00:33:54.366 --> 00:33:56.368
[panting]

711
00:33:56.535 --> 00:33:57.703
[gasps]

712
00:33:57.828 --> 00:34:00.205
You tell Raq it was Kanan.

713
00:34:00.706 --> 00:34:01.790
Got it?

714
00:34:02.708 --> 00:34:03.792
[grunts]

715
00:34:04.334 --> 00:34:05.502
Kanan.

716
00:34:07.379 --> 00:34:09.172
Say that shit out loud. bitch.

717
00:34:09.715 --> 00:34:10.966
Kanan.

718
00:34:11.759 --> 00:34:13.177
Get the fuck outta here.

719
00:34:13.302 --> 00:34:15.137
[Kirsten sobbing]

720
00:34:17.764 --> 00:34:21.018
[music transitions
into grim. tense music]

721
00:34:35.239 --> 00:34:36.742
[car engine starts]

722
00:34:37.951 --> 00:34:39.661
[gunshots]

723
00:34:45.751 --> 00:34:47.085
[music fades]

724
00:34:47.252 --> 00:34:48.730
They switched out the coke
I was bringing to him

725
00:34:48.754 --> 00:34:49.797
with something else.

726
00:34:49.963 --> 00:34:51.255
I don't know what the fuck
it was

727
00:34:51.422 --> 00:34:52.674
but he died.

728
00:34:52.841 --> 00:34:54.426
Right in front of me.
It was horrible.

729
00:34:54.592 --> 00:34:56.428
It was so fucked up. [sniffles]

730
00:34:57.012 --> 00:34:58.680
And they just grabbed you
off the street?

731
00:34:58.847 --> 00:35:00.057
In front of the club.

732
00:35:00.766 --> 00:35:01.993
And then the kid
who was in charge.

733
00:35:02.017 --> 00:35:03.727
he told me
to tell you something.

734
00:35:04.311 --> 00:35:05.854
He said. "Tell Raq
it was Kanan."

735
00:35:06.021 --> 00:35:08.023
He really wanted you
to know that.

736
00:35:08.774 --> 00:35:10.484
Nobody else gonna hear
about that part.

737
00:35:10.901 --> 00:35:11.901
That stay between us.

738
00:35:11.944 --> 00:35:13.028
Whatever.

739
00:35:13.195 --> 00:35:14.988
I'm never doing this shit again.
I'm done.

740
00:35:15.155 --> 00:35:17.199
You tell anybody else.
especially Flossie.

741
00:35:17.366 --> 00:35:18.784
about what that boy said.

742
00:35:18.951 --> 00:35:21.054
I'ma have to do somethin' to you
that can't be undone.

743
00:35:21.078 --> 00:35:22.538
[dramatic music playing]

744
00:35:22.704 --> 00:35:23.956
Understood?

745
00:35:27.501 --> 00:35:30.003
You did right when you came
to me like you did.

746
00:35:30.128 --> 00:35:33.131
And where I'm from.
righteousness gets rewarded.

747
00:35:34.800 --> 00:35:36.927
This is twice
what she was paying you

748
00:35:37.052 --> 00:35:38.846
and you deserve
every penny of it.

749
00:35:39.012 --> 00:35:40.347
And the best part?

750
00:35:40.514 --> 00:35:42.432
You don't gotta split it up
three ways anymore.

751
00:35:42.599 --> 00:35:44.101
[Stefano chuckles]

752
00:35:44.226 --> 00:35:45.352
Thank you kindly. sir.

753
00:35:45.769 --> 00:35:47.521
Now. Giorgio's gonna show you
out to the car

754
00:35:47.688 --> 00:35:49.106
we got waiting for you.

755
00:35:49.273 --> 00:35:52.150
And. uh. safe travels.
my friend.

756
00:35:59.116 --> 00:36:01.702
[chuckles]

757
00:36:05.163 --> 00:36:07.457
[ominous music playing]

758
00:36:08.375 --> 00:36:09.960
-Aw. fu...
-[silenced gunshot]

759
00:36:10.085 --> 00:36:11.712
[casing clatters]

760
00:36:18.218 --> 00:36:21.221
-[music fades]
-["What You In It For" plays]

761
00:36:21.388 --> 00:36:23.932
♪ It's my season
I don't need a reason ♪

762
00:36:24.099 --> 00:36:26.560
♪ Takeover time
I'm tired of all this treason ♪

763
00:36:26.727 --> 00:36:28.896
♪ Street life. trife life
Cutthroat season ♪

764
00:36:29.062 --> 00:36:31.106
Breeze says you was short
the other day.

765
00:36:31.273 --> 00:36:34.234
♪ Niggas stuck in the game
They never gon' leave it ♪

766
00:36:34.401 --> 00:36:35.819
♪ Eye for an eye. nigga... ♪

767
00:36:35.986 --> 00:36:38.071
You're so fuckin' stupid. Kanan.

768
00:36:38.947 --> 00:36:40.908
You can't even see
that nigga playin' you.

769
00:36:43.118 --> 00:36:44.453
Breeze want us beefin'

770
00:36:45.412 --> 00:36:47.664
so he can see
who come out on top.

771
00:36:50.918 --> 00:36:52.419
And I'm good with that.

772
00:36:52.586 --> 00:36:54.880
♪ Can't be broke
When I got Cain and Abel ♪

773
00:36:55.047 --> 00:36:56.298
Real good.

774
00:36:56.465 --> 00:36:57.925
♪ Ain't no Motherfuckin' fable ♪

775
00:36:58.091 --> 00:36:59.527
♪ Saabs and ACs
Lamb skins on my back ♪

